        <h3 class="config-card__title">方式 1: 使用内置模式（最简单）</h3>
        <p class="config-card__desc">直接指定模式名称，使用内置的默认配置。</p>

        <div class="ch-code-block">
          <pre><code><span class="code-tag">&lt;FlowDesigner</span> <span class="code-attr">mode</span>=<span class="code-string">"design"</span> <span class="code-tag">/&gt;</span></code></pre>
        </div>

        <div class="ch-callout ch-callout--info">
          <strong>适用场景：</strong>快速原型开发，标准场景
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 方式2: 部分覆盖 -->
      <div class="config-card">
        <h3 class="config-card__title">方式 2: 部分覆盖权限（推荐）</h3>
        <p class="config-card__desc">通过 <code>permissionConfig</code> 覆盖需要修改的权限。</p>

        <div class="ch-code-block">
          <pre><code><span class="code-tag">&lt;FlowDesigner</span>
  <span class="code-attr">mode</span>=<span class="code-string">"readonly"</span>
  <span class="code-attr">:permissionConfig</span>=<span class="code-string">"</span>{
    readonly: {
      showToolbar: <span class="code-boolean">false</span>,
      canAddNode: <span class="code-boolean">false</span>,
      canDrag: <span class="code-boolean">false</span>
    }
  }<span class="code-string">"</span>
<span class="code-tag">/&gt;</span></code></pre>
        </div>

        <div class="ch-callout ch-callout--info">
          <strong>适用场景：</strong>在内置模式基础上少量调整
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 方式3: 完全自定义 -->
      <div class="config-card">
        <h3 class="config-card__title">方式 3: 完全自定义（最灵活）</h3>
        <p class="config-card__desc">通过 <code>getPermissions</code> 函数完全接管权限计算。</p>
        <p class="config-card__desc" style="color: red">注意：通过getPermissions函数完全接管权限，permissionConfig参数配置的权限将会失效，所有权限默认都为false, 需要对应的权限必须显式地置为true</p>

        <div class="ch-code-block">
          <pre><code><span class="code-tag">&lt;FlowDesigner</span>
  <span class="code-attr">:getPermissions</span>=<span class="code-string">"</span>(mode) => ({
    ...basePermissions,
    canDrag: userRole === <span class="code-string">'admin'</span>
  })<span class="code-string">"</span>
<span class="code-tag">/&gt;</span></code></pre>
        </div>
        <CodePreviewer demo-name="demo-permission-getPermission" />
        <div class="ch-callout ch-callout--info">
          <strong>适用场景：</strong>根据用户角色/流程状态动态计算权限
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 优先级说明 -->
