          <div class="priority-step">
            <div class="priority-step__num">1</div>
            <div class="priority-step__content">
              <strong>内置默认</strong>
              <p>builtinPermissionPresets[mode]</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="priority-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="priority-step">
            <div class="priority-step__num">2</div>
            <div class="priority-step__content">
              <strong>permissionConfig</strong>
              <p>模式-权限映射表覆盖</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="priority-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="priority-step priority-step--special">
            <div class="priority-step__num">*</div>
            <div class="priority-step__content">
              <strong>getPermissions</strong>
              <p>完全接管（忽略其他配置）</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ch-callout ch-callout--warning">
          <strong>注意：</strong>
          <ul>
            <li>如果提供了 <code>getPermissions</code>，将忽略所有其他配置</li>
            <li>后面的配置会覆盖前面的同名权限</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
